text: Carl Johan Thyselius (8 June 1811 - 11 January 1891) was a Swedish politician and government official. He served as Justice Councillor (1856-1860), Minister for Ecclesiastical Affairs (1860-1863), Minister for Civil Affairs (responsible for trade, industry and ship transport (1875-80), and he served as the Prime Minister from 1883 to 1884. == References == Category:1811 births Category:1891 deaths Category:Government ministers of Sweden Category:Prime ministers of Sweden
title: Carl Johan Thyselius
